{"tid":1915230,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"袁國勇：疫情不會完結，到夏天情況可能會有改善，但病毒會傳到南半球，到冬天又會再有外地輸入個案","createTime":"2020-03-08T05:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T06:50:40.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a359a14614f5418856fc93d4f132b5a7501bfbfd","tid":1915230,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"袁國勇表示，新型冠狀病毒疫情不會完結，到夏天情況可能會有改善，但病毒會傳到南半球，到冬天又會再有外地輸入個案，他呼籲市民如非必要，不要外遊，注意個人衛生，形容守得越久，防疫物資就越多，研發出疫苗和抗病毒藥物的機會也越大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fa2160ced232e2ff322b69db833b22c25400cf","tid":1915230,"uid":220451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:21:06.000Z","msg":"支爆 支爆"},{"pid":"08a5517abd226187a4707a928cde8e78a6494b12","tid":1915230,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHyYi2E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHyYi2E.gif&h=b8cb24c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65091ba8a4287776b4ec52fe70d1ff4a9725c4f4","tid":1915230,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"袁國勇：新型冠狀病毒疫情不會完結<br />\n08.03.2020 11:30<br />\n港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇表示，新型冠狀病毒疫情不會完結，到夏天情況可能會有改善，但病毒會傳到南半球，到冬天又會再有外地輸入個案，他呼籲市民如非必要，不要外遊，注意個人衛生，形容守得越久，防疫物資就越多，研發出疫苗和抗病毒藥物的機會也越大，可以減低社區傳播，避免公立醫院癱瘓。袁國勇在一個電視台節目表示，視乎疫情的階段，圍堵和紓緩策略可以同時進行，如果市民已經學懂注意手部衛生，正確佩戴口罩，保持社交距離，到時恢復上學或上班也不成問題。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇又表示，隨著海外越來越多確診個案，是否對內地封關已經不重要，政府對外地實施入境限制時，不應只注意當地的確診數字，還要留意有多少輸入個案，未來要注意由印度入境的人，也要留意南亞人士聚居的地方有沒有確診個案。他又指，新型冠狀病毒的斷症並不容易，希望更多私家診所可以協助收集疑似患者的樣本，可以更清楚掌握本港情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1272261\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1272261&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5BwwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=5fe3d4ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1272261</a>"},{"pid":"d75ecd398ba5e2cee153e6c99d199e0b160c816f","tid":1915230,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"又話半年有疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d72cf75b469c9da40b481c6bf71029d8a88fdf","tid":1915230,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d75ecd398ba5e2cee153e6c99d199e0b160c816f","tid":1915230,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"又話半年有疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"流浮山刀手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcc72ea3fa9c184f6fadb79100d8d8c52ff8fe7","tid":1915230,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7526fa023c619dc6dfde88d1d5965a5567e8e8ae","tid":1915230,"uid":307315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"佢真係up 得就up ，唔洗research，唔洗study ，唔洗專家嗰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明大把外媒叫唔好ff夏天疫情會減，個個都寫乜highly uncertain 呀， no evidence showing"}]}